{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Despite being Jewish, he was the best in class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So he was brilliant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he had his clogs, and the clogs running bruised-- bruised his-- his legs terribly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the legs got infected with the sand and cement, and they got terribly swollen, full with pus.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "So in the evening, he went to the so-called Krankenbau, which is hospital in English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "There were every evening about 600, 800 people standing, trying to get in, and every evening they admitted about 30 or 40.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "So 5% got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We had to be really terribly sick to get in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But anyhow, he went up queuing there four times, and the fourth time, they let him in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They let him in, and he got treatment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Why I'm telling it is because after a few weeks they selected him-- officers came, and they picked him out and 28 other boys for medical experimentation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They picked him out and the others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And then after one week, he came back with all-- all his leg was full with pus.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And they injected all sorts of bacteria in him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "So they had to cut off-- they had to amputate his leg after about two weeks when that happening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So his leg-- his leg was amputated, but he was still alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to visit him sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came my turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After about seven or eight weeks, very early in August, my leg was also bruised.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dirt went into it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Badly swollen, full with pus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I just did the same what my friend did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went every evening trying to get in, trying to get in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, by some miracle, eventually the third or fourth night they let me into the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got into the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
